INSERT INTO `models` VALUES ('1', 'OO9102 HOLBROOK', '1', '1', '1', '1', 'Designed by snowboarding superstar Shaun White and his brother Jesse to represent the screen heroes from the 40s, 50s, and 60s, these Holbrook sunglasses are timeless classics. Featuring metal bolts, icons that highlight the stress-resistant O MATTER¬Æ frames, and PLUTONITE¬Æ lenses used to filter out the UV rays, Oakley has designed a pair of sunglasses that will give you that Hollywood look with unparalleled comfort.'), ('2', 'PR 06MS', '2', '1', '2', '2', 'The hallmark styling of this world-renowned fashion leader denotes high quality with a dedication to innovation and a strong tradition of craftsmanship. Prada is synonymous with an understated style that has always anticipated, and often dictated, new trends. Prada sunglasses use only the finest materials to strike the ideal balance of form and function.'), ('3', 'PO2376S', '3', '2', '3', '3', 'Designed and crafted in Italy, Persol - from the Italian \"per il sole\" meaning \"for the sun\" - is a favorite among tastemakers and celebrities for its impeccable fit and incredible clarity. The brand\'s patented Meflecto temples offer a secure fit, while crystal-tempered sunglass lenses provide protection with distortion-free vision. With a brand character that can best be described as classy, exclusive, stylish, and unique, Persol continues to go beyond trends.'), ('4', 'OVERHANG', '4', '1', '1', '1', 'For those with a passion for excellence, Revo sunglasses offer superior lens technology to enhance your view of the world. The Revo Light Management System, derived from NASA technology, works like a graphic equalizer, providing optimal vision and performance. The result is stunning, sharper, clearer views of the world. Revo is designed for the innovator who is individualistic -- a leader, not a follower.'), ('5', 'HIGHSIDE L', '4', '1', '1', '1', 'Sustainability on a whole new level. Revo Polarcast‚Ñ¢ Infused Performance Serilium‚Ñ¢ lenses. Ele